Notice:
If you have miniconda installed, make sure,in your $PATH variable, /usr/bin/perl is before   the dir of minicoda/bin/

===================================================================================
usage
===================================================================================
perl  GenomeCutter.pl Enzyme.list.txt genome.fasta -Min 2000 (the minimum length of contig used for enzyme cutting)
===================================================================================

